              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A multiwire proportional counter (MWPC)",
                "filled with 370-Pa isobutane was placed before the",
                "focal plane detector (FPD) to distinguish",
                "implantation events from radioactive decay events in",
                "FPD."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Focal plane detector consisted of Si detectors",
                "with 48 vertical strips to measure positional",
                "information of implantation and decay events."
              ]
            }
          ],
